{"tid":1419022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍衫同白衫 - 有啲說話同你地講","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:49:08.000Z","uid":142314,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3a31e984e311397ec9c3f7484aa7e9fcd3eb8e","tid":1419022,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:03:16.000Z","msg":"義士經過一連串示威，黑警full gear 由初初都驚，變成而家乜都唔驚，你地幾耐冇打過交，用打機黎講，你地最多比市民多小小lvl,可能lvl 10, 但義士已經升lvl去到99了。<br />\n<br />\n而最重要一點係你地收左錢做野，一個同行落單比人捉走左，你地自己只會逃走，因為最重要既係錢，公義、手足情對你地黎講係唔及錢重要。昨晚你地有人落單，成班人可以就咁走左去。<br />\n<br />\n相反，如果示威者有一個手足落單，大家係會救援，甚至圍警局。<br />\n<br />\n你地如果打傷任何一位手足，大家一定十倍奉還！！你地同伴一定唔會救你地任何一個人！"},{"pid":"57bc8717b0a5e1e21045341076eaa6b16e287e89","tid":1419022,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:04:10.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7999feb3b5a583329624f221b1e04f8200781f4","tid":1419022,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:31:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"472bf250cac5752c32a625d18c6bfbb876d378ff","tid":1419022,"uid":127858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1af3586d07a403ae3cd4cbe0dbae58ce0c5658f6","tid":1419022,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"你班仆街而家先浦頭<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0NRUq1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0NRUq1.png&h=e13d97ab&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}